platforms   darwin
use_bzip2   yes

long_description \
        Libassuan is a small library implementing the so-called \
        Assuan protocol. This protocol is used for IPC between \
        most newer GnuPG components. Both, server and client side \
        functions are provided.

master_sites    gnupg

